 &gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt;090528  6:46:26 - mysqld got signal 11 ;
 &gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt;This could be because you hit a bug. It is also possible 
that
 &gt;&gt; this
 &gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &gt;binary
